## Short-Form Copy Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define the goal: what action should the reader take?
- [ ] 2. Identify the one key benefit or differentiator
- [ ] 3. Write multiple options rapidly
- [ ] 4. Test and iterate on word choice and structure
- [ ] 5. Finalize copy that is specific, clear, and compelling

## Key Inputs
- Format: {{format}} (headline, tagline, social post, ad copy, CTA)
- Product/Service: {{product_service}}
- Key Benefit: {{key_benefit}}
- Audience: {{audience}}
- Tone: {{tone}}
